invalid type: string "Multi-Intent Queries\nQ1. My payment failed and I want to cancel order\nA. Retry payment or cancel before shipment.\nQ2. I want refund and also exchange product\nA. Choose either refund or exchange as per policy.\nQ3. Change address and delivery date\nA. Address can be updated before shipping; delivery date depends on carrier.\nQ4. Cancel order and apply coupon again\n’’’’’’’